{"lemma":"حُطامٌ","slug":"حُطامٌ","root":"ح.ط.م","root_slug":"ح-ط-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ط-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حُطام","root":"حطم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8396","n8400"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"debris, ruins","tags":["uncountable"],"examples":[{"text":"حُطَامُ ٱلسُّفُنِ","english":"shipwreck"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From حَطَمَ (ḥaṭama, “to crash, to crease, to crack”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8396","headword_ar":"حُطَامٌ","root":"HTm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is broken in pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing that"},{"kind":"page_break","n":595},{"kind":"text","text":"is dry, or tough. (S, K. [In the CK, by the accidental omission of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa kaguraAbK","text_ar":"وَ كَغُرَابٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", this signification and the next here following, from the K, are assigned to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaEodapN HiTamN","text_ar":"صَعْدَةٌ حِطَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiTomapN","text_ar":"حِطْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which, accord. to some copies of the K, is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuTaAmN","text_ar":"حُطَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense explained above.]) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fragments"},{"kind":"text","text":"of eggs; (A, TA;) or of an egg-shell; so in a verse of Et-Tirimmáh: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shell"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the egg. (K.) ―         -b2-  [See a tropical usage of it in an ex. cited, from a trad., voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAmN","text_ar":"ثُمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuTaAmu Ald~unoyaA","text_ar":"حُطَامُ الدُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The frail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perishing, goods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessions, of the present world:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Z, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuTaAmN","text_ar":"حُطَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying the “ fragments ” of eggs: (TA:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the goods of the present world."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErD","text_ar":"عرض"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n8400","headword_ar":"حَطَّامٌ","root":"HTm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaTuwmN","text_ar":"حَطُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuTamN","text_ar":"حُطَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}